caption.body: Pacific Southwest Airlines (PSA) featured San Francisco in this circa 1968 postcard, the back of which reads, “Flying with PSA – The Nation’s Leading Intra-State Airline – Over the Golden Gate Bridge”. Gerald French Pacific Southwest Airlines (PSA) postcard c. 1968 SFO Museum Collection Gift of David Winckoski 2011.195.046
